<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 96-12-27 - Announcing Latest Field Service Components For T 444E Engines Model Years 1994-1996</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi961227" tsitype="engine">
        <tsinumber>96-12-27</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>October 1996</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>ENGINE</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Announcing Latest Field Service Components For T 444E Engines Model Years 1994-1996</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <engfamgroup/>

                <engfam>T 444E</engfam>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <svcproc svcproctype="TSI" graphiccount="0">
            <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
            <svcprocinfo>
                <para>The following items are updated and released for field service on T 444E engines Model Years 1994
                    thru 1996:
                </para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>Skeleton and Stripped Service Engines</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>Crankcase Assembly/Service Package</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>Oil Pan Assembly/Service Package</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>Piston and Ring Packages And Cylinder Head Gasket/Service Packages</para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
                <para>New skeleton (short block) service engine,
                    <emph type="bold">P/N 1830847C91</emph>, incorporates a new crankcase, pistons, rings and cam
                    follower guides which are the latest designed parts used on 1997 Model Year T 444E engines.
                </para>
                <para>The new stripped service engine,
                    <emph type="bold">P/N 1830846C91</emph>, includes new skeleton engine changes plus, new crankcase
                    front cover, oil pan and oil pick-up tube. These parts are also the latest parts released for 1997
                    Model Year T 444E engines.
                </para>
                <para>New crankcase assembly service package,
                    <emph type="bold">P/N 1830845C91</emph>, is also furnished with eight cam follower guide assemblies.
                    The new guide assemblies replace the previous guides, guide retainers, and fasteners. The service
                    package is furnished with guide replacement instructions.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>The new guide assemblies
                            <emph type="bold">must be</emph>
                            used with the new crankcase, due to design changes.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
                <para>New oil pan assembly service package,
                    <emph type="bold">P/N 1830836C91</emph>, is also furnished with the oil level gauge tube adapter,
                    adapter retainer and o-ring. Assemble these parts before installing the oil pan; refer to
                    instructions included with the service package.
                </para>
                <para>Refer to the following for piston and ring packages and cylinder head gasket/package part
                    numbers.
                </para>
            </svcprocinfo>
            <svcsubproc>
                <title>PISTON AND RINGS SERVICE PACKAGES:</title>
                <para>Each Package Consists of the Following Parts</para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>(1) Piston</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(3) Piston Rings</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(1) Piston Pin</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(2) Piston Pin Retainers</para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
                <para>
                    <emph type="bold">Package Part Nos:</emph>
                </para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>(Standard Size)
                            <emph type="bold">1824166C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(.010 Oversize)
                            <emph type="bold">1826699C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(.020 Oversize)
                            <emph type="bold">1826700C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(.030 Oversize)
                            <emph type="bold">1826701C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
            </svcsubproc>
            <svcsubproc>
                <title>PISTON RINGS SERVICE PACKAGES:</title>
                <para>Each Package Consists of the Following Parts</para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>(1) Top Compression Ring</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(1) Intermediate Compression Ring</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(1) Oil Control Ring</para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
                <para>
                    <emph type="bold">Package Part Nos:</emph>
                </para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>(Standard Size)
                            <emph type="bold">1824162C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(.010 Oversize)
                            <emph type="bold">1824163C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(.020 Oversize)
                            <emph type="bold">1824164C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(.030 Oversize)
                            <emph type="bold">1824165C91</emph>
                        </para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
            </svcsubproc>
            <svcsubproc>
                <title>CYLINDER HEAD GASKET</title>
                <para>
                    <emph type="bold">Part No: 1825289C1</emph>
                </para>
            </svcsubproc>
            <svcsubproc>
                <title>CYLINDER HEAD GASKET PACKAGE:</title>
                <para>Package Includes Two Head Gaskets ONLY</para>
                <para>
                    <emph type="bold">Package Part No: 1824161C91</emph>
                </para>
            </svcsubproc>
            <svcsubproc>
                <title>CYLINDER HEAD GASKET PACKAGE:</title>
                <para>Package Consists of the Following Parts</para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>(2) Head Gaskets</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(16) Valve Seals</para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>(1) Instruction Sheet</para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
                <para>
                    <emph type="bold">Package Part No: 1824158C91</emph>
                </para>
            </svcsubproc>
        </svcproc>
    </tsi>
